        public static final java.lang.String HEALTH_STATUS
        the project health status. Example include Green, Yellow, Red. Green means that the project is under control and is proceeding as planned on the schedule. Yellow means that a project is somewhat behind schedule or somewhat at risk. Red means the project is in trouble (over budget or behind schedule).
